und text-balance max-w-2xl mx-auto\">The safest way to close a resale home</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-lg text-[var(--text-secondary)] max-w-xl mx-auto text-balance\">SafeBuy is built for Indian resale: escrow-protected payments, lawyer-led diligence, and a door-to-door closing handled online.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-white p-7 flex flex-col\" style=\"box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"relative w-full h-32 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden mb-6\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent) 0%, #ffffff 75%)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(to right, #e6ebf1 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to bottom, #e6ebf1 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:24px 24px;opacity:0.35;mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 30%, transparent 75%)\"></div><div class=\"relative w-14 h-14 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center\" style=\"background:#ffffff;border:1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 20%, transparent);box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-slot=\"icon\" class=\"w-7 h-7\" style=\"color:var(--primary)\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 0 1 3.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 0 0 3 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285Z\"></path></svg></div></div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-2\">Engineered for safety</p><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground tracking-tight\">Your money sits in escrow</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed\">Every rupee flows through an ICICI Bank escrow account. Funds release to the seller only after each legal milestone clears — never before.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-white p-7 flex flex-col\" style=\"box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"relative w-full h-32 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden mb-6\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--warning-subtle) 0%, #ffffff 75%)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(to right, #e6ebf1 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to bottom, #e6ebf1 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:24px 24px;opacity:0.35;mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 30%, transparent 75%)\"></div><div class=\"relative w-14 h-14 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center\" style=\"background:#ffffff;border:1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--warning) 20%, transparent);box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-slot=\"icon\" class=\"w-7 h-7\" style=\"color:var(--warning)\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 3v17.25m0 0c-1.472 0-2.882.265-4.185.75M12 20.25c1.472 0 2.882.265 4.185.75M18.75 4.97A48.416 48.416 0 0 0 12 4.5c-2.291 0-4.545.16-6.75.47m13.5 0c1.01.143 2.01.317 3 .52m-3-.52 2.62 10.726c.122.499-.106 1.028-.589 1.202a5.988 5.988 0 0 1-2.031.352 5.988 5.988 0 0 1-2.031-.352c-.483-.174-.711-.703-.59-1.202L18.75 4.971Zm-16.5.52c.99-.203 1.99-.377 3-.52m0 0 2.62 10.726c.122.499-.106 1.028-.589 1.202a5.989 5.989 0 0 1-2.031.352 5.989 5.989 0 0 1-2.031-.352c-.483-.174-.711-.703-.59-1.202L5.25 4.971Z\"></path></svg></div></div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-2\">Built on legal diligence</p><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground tracking-tight\">Every document, verified</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed\">Our lawyers trace ownership back 30 years, pull the encumbrance certificate, and verify khata, tax, and sanctioned plans — in a plain-English report.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-white p-7 flex flex-col\" style=\"box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"relative w-full h-32 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden mb-6\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--success-subtle) 0%, #ffffff 75%)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(to right, #e6ebf1 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to bottom, #e6ebf1 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:24px 24px;opacity:0.35;mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 30%, transparent 75%)\"></div><div class=\"relative w-14 h-14 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center\" style=\"background:#ffffff;border:1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--success) 20%, transparent);box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-slot=\"icon\" class=\"w-7 h-7\" style=\"color:var(--success)\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10.5 1.5H8.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 6 3.75v16.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25h7.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 18 20.25V3.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25H13.5m-3 0V3h3V1.5m-3 0h3m-3 18.75h3\"></path></svg></div></div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-2\">Designed for simplicity</p><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground tracking-tight\">Closed from your phone</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed\">We run the paperwork, bank calls, and sub-registrar coordination over WhatsApp. You show up once — to sign at the SRO, as the law requires.</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"how-it-works\" class=\"section-wrapper bg-[var(--surface)]\"><div class=\"container-lg px-6 md:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><span class=\"eyebrow\">How it works</span><h2 class=\"mt-4 text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground text-balance max-w-2xl mx-auto\">From lock-in to<!-- --> <span class=\"text-[var(--primary)]\">keys in hand</span></h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-lg text-[var(--text-secondary)] max-w-xl mx-auto text-balance\">Four clear steps, 21 days door to door. Start with the full journey, or pick a single service for one step.</p></div><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-start mb-16\"><ol class=\"space-y-2\" style=\"opacity:0\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl cursor-pointer transition-all duration-300 bg-white border border-[var(--border)] shadow-[var(--shadow-md)]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold transition-colors\" style=\"background:var(--primary);border:2px solid var(--primary);color:#fff\">1</div><div class=\"flex-1 pt-0.5 min-w-0\"><p class=\"text-[0.65rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-0.5\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono)\">01</p><p class=\"font-semibold text-foreground tracking-tight mb-1\">Lock in the home</p><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed\" style=\"opacity:0;height:0px\">Confirm the terms and park your token in a Jumbo SafeBuy escrow account. Fully refundable until legal diligence clears — so your money moves only when the deal is safe.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl cursor-pointer transition-all duration-300 opacity-50 hover:opacity-75\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold transition-colors\" style=\"background:var(--surface);border:2px solid var(--border);color:var(--text-muted)\">2</div><div class=\"flex-1 pt-0.5 min-w-0\"><p class=\"text-[0.65rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-0.5\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono)\">02</p><p class=\"font-semibold text-foreground tracking-tight mb-1\">We verify everything</p></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl cursor-pointer transition-all duration-300 opacity-50 hover:opacity-75\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold transition-colors\" style=\"background:var(--surface);border:2px solid var(--border);color:var(--text-muted)\">3</div><div class=\"flex-1 pt-0.5 min-w-0\"><p class=\"text-[0.65rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-0.5\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono)\">03</p><p class=\"font-semibold text-foreground tracking-tight mb-1\">Sign the paperwork online</p></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl cursor-pointer transition-all duration-300 opacity-50 hover:opacity-75\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold transition-colors\" style=\"background:var(--surface);border:2px solid var(--border);color:var(--text-muted)\">4</div><div class=\"flex-1 pt-0.5 min-w-0\"><p class=\"text-[0.65rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-0.5\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono)\">04</p><p class=\"font-semibold text-foreground tracking-tight mb-1\">Transfer and move in</p></div></li></ol><div class=\"relative lg:sticky lg:top-24 flex items-center justify-center min-h-72\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.97)\"><div class=\"relative w-full aspect-square max-w-sm rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] overflow-hidden\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent) 0%, #ffffff 65%);box-shadow:var(--shadow-md)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(to right, #e6ebf1 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to bottom, #e6ebf1 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:28px 28px;opacity:0.35;mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 30%, transparent 80%)\"></div><div class=\"relative w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center p-10\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-[16rem] flex flex-col items-stretch gap-3\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-white p-4 flex items-center gap-3\" style=\"box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm)\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-slot=\"icon\" class=\"w-5 h-5\" style=\"color:var(--primary)\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M8.25 21v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21m0 0h4.5V3.545M12.75 21h7.5V10.75M2.25 21h1.5m18 0h-18M2.25 9l4.5-1.636M18.75 3l-1.5.545m0 6.205 3 1m1.5.5-1.5-.5M6.75 7.364V3h-3v18m3-13.636 10.5-3.819\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"min-w-0\"><p class=\"text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Property</p><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-foreground truncate\">HSR Layout, Bangalore</p></div></div><div class=\"flex justify-center\"><div class=\"w-px h-5 bg-[var(--border-strong)]\"></div></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-white p-4 flex items-center gap-3\" style=\"box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm)\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\" style=\"background:var(--success-subtle)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-slot=\"icon\" class=\"w-5 h-5\" style=\"color:var(--success)\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0 1 15.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 0 1 3 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 0 0-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 0 0 3 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5Zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5Z\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"min-w-0 flex-1\"><p class=\"text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Escrow</p><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-foreground\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono)\">₹1,00,000 locked</p></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-slot=\"icon\" class=\"w-5 h-5 shrink-0\" style=\"color:var(--success)\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 0 1-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 0 1-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 12 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 0 1-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 0 1-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 3 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 0 1 1.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 0 1 3.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0 1 12 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 0 1 3.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 0 1 1.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 21 12Z\"></path></svg></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex gap-1.5\"><button class=\"h-1.5 rounded-full transition-all duration-300\" style=\"width:1.25rem;background:var(--primary)\" aria-label=\"Go to step 1\"></button><button class=\"h-1.5 rounded-full transition-all duration-300\" style=\"width:0.375rem;background:var(--border-strong)\" aria-label=\"Go to step 2\"></button><button class=\"h-1.5 rounded-full transition-all duration-300\" style=\"width:0.375rem;background:var(--border-strong)\" aria-label=\"Go to step 3\"></button><button class=\"h-1.5 rounded-full transition-all duration-300\" style=\"width:0.375rem;background:var(--border-strong)\" aria-label=\"Go to step 4\"></button></div></div></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-white p-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-6\" style=\"box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-foreground tracking-tight\">Just need help with one thing?</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">Browse our catalog of 20+ individual services. Fixed prices, clear results, no bundling required.</p></div><a class=\"shrink-0 inline-flex items-center gap-2 h-10 px-5 rounded-md border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] text-sm font-semibold text-foreground hover:border-[var(--border-strong)] hover:bg-white transition-colors\" href=\"/services\">Browse all services<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-slot=\"icon\" class=\"w-4 h-4\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3\"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section id=\"features\" class=\"section-wrapper\"><div class=\"container-lg px-6 md:px-8\"><div class=\"mb-14\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><span class=\"eyebrow\">Why SafeBuy</span><h2 class=\"mt-4 text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground text-balance max-w-2xl\">The guardrails your biggest purchase deserves</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-lg text-[var(--text-secondary)] max-w-xl text-balance\">Purpose-built for Indian resale: every rupee in escrow, every document verified, every closing tracked door to door.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-4\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-2 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-white p-7 flex flex-col justify-between\" style=\"box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6\" style=\"background:var(--success-subtle)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-slot=\"icon\" class=\"w-5 h-5\" style=\"color:var(--success)\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 0 1 3.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 0 0 3 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285Z\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-1\" style=\"color:var(--success);font-family:var(--font-mono)\">₹0<span class=\"text-2xl ml-1 text-[var(--text-muted)] font-medium\">lost to fraud</span></p><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-foreground tracking-tight mt-2\">Zero fraud, across every rupee</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed\">Every transaction we&#x27;ve processed has cleared without a single rupee of fraud loss. That&#x27;s not luck — it&#x27;s escrow, legal diligence, and 21 days of structured transfer.</p></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-2 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-white p-7 flex flex-col\" style=\"box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"w-full rounded-lg border border-[var(--border)] p-4 mb-5 flex items-center justify-between\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent) 0%, #ffffff 70%)\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1.5\"><div class=\"w-11 h-11 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center\" style=\"background:#ffffff;border:1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--text-secondary) 20%, transparent);box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-slot=\"icon\" class=\"w-5 h-5\" style=\"color:var(--text-secondary)\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0ZM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0 1 14.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632Z\"></path></svg></div><p class=\"text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--text-muted)]\">You</p><div class=\"absolute -z-10 w-16 h-16 rounded-full blur-2xl opacity-0\" style=\"background:var(--surface)\"></div></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-slot=\"icon\" class=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[var(--text-muted)] shrink-0\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1.5\"><div class=\"w-11 h-11 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center\" style=\"background:#ffffff;border:1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 20%, transparent);box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-slot=\"icon\" class=\"w-5 h-5\" style=\"color:var(--primary)\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 21v-8.25M15.75 21v-8.25M8.25 21v-8.25M3 9l9-6 9 6m-1.5 12V10.332A48.36 48.36 0 0 0 12 9.75c-2.551 0-5.056.2-7.5.582V21M3 21h18M12 6.75h.008v.008H12V6.75Z\"></path></svg></div><p class=\"text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--text-muted)]\">ICICI escrow</p><div class=\"absolute -z-10 w-16 h-16 rounded-full blur-2xl opacity-0\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"></div></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-slot=\"icon\" class=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[var(--text-muted)] shrink-0\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1.5\"><div class=\"w-11 h-11 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center\" style=\"background:#ffffff;border:1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--text-secondary) 20%, transparent);box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-slot=\"icon\" class=\"w-5 h-5\" style=\"color:var(--text-secondary)\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0ZM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0 1 14.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632Z\"></path></svg></div><p class=\"text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--text-muted)]\">Seller</p><div class=\"absolute -z-10 w-16 h-16 rounded-full blur-2xl opacity-0\" style=\"background:var(--surface)\"></div></div></div><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-foreground tracking-tight\">Your money sits with ICICI, not us</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed\">All payments flow through a Jumbo SafeBuy escrow account held at ICICI Bank. Funds are released to the seller only after legal milestones are signed off — never before.</p></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-2 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-white p-7 flex flex-col\" style=\"box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"w-full rounded-lg border border-[var(--border)] p-4 mb-5 flex flex-col gap-2\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent) 0%, #ffffff 70%)\"><div class=\"self-start max-w-[85%] rounded-2xl rounded-bl-md bg-white border border-[var(--border)] px-3 py-2 flex items-start gap-2\" style=\"box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-slot=\"icon\" class=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 mt-0.5 shrink-0\" style=\"color:var(--primary)\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M20.25 8.511c.884.284 1.5 1.128 1.5 2.097v4.286c0 1.136-.847 2.1-1.98 2.193-.34.027-.68.052-1.02.072v3.091l-3-3c-1.354 0-2.694-.055-4.02-.163a2.115 2.115 0 0 1-.825-.242m9.345-8.334a2.126 2.126 0 0 0-.476-.095 48.64 48.64 0 0 0-8.048 0c-1.131.094-1.976 1.057-1.976 2.192v4.286c0 .837.46 1.58 1.155 1.951m9.345-8.334V6.637c0-1.621-1.152-3.026-2.76-3.235A48.455 48.455 0 0 0 11.25 3c-2.115 0-4.198.137-6.24.402-1.608.209-2.76 1.614-2.76 3.235v6.226c0 1.621 1.152 3.026 2.76 3.235.577.075 1.157.14 1.74.194V21l4.155-4.155\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-xs text-foreground leading-snug\">SRO appointment booked for Fri, 11:30 AM.</p></div><div class=\"self-end inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-2xl rounded-br-md px-3 py-1.5\" style=\"background:var(--success-subtle);border:1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--success) 20%, transparent)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-slot=\"icon\" class=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" style=\"color:var(--success)\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 0 1-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 0 1-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 12 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 0 1-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 0 1-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 3 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 0 1 1.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 0 1 3.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0 1 12 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 0 1 3.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 0 1 1.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 21 12Z\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold\" style=\"color:var(--success)\">Confirmed</p></div></div><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-foreground tracking-tight\">Handled from your phone</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed\">We run the paperwork, bank calls, and sub-registrar coordination. You show up once — to sign at the SRO, as the law requires. Everything else happens over WhatsApp and email.</p></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-3 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-white p-7 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start gap-5\" style=\"box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\" style=\"background:var(--warning-subtle)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-slot=\"icon\" class=\"w-5 h-5\" style=\"color:var(--warning)\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0 1 15.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 0 1 3 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 0 0-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 0 0 3 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5Zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5Z\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-0.5\" style=\"color:var(--warning);font-family:var(--font-mono)\">90+<span class=\"text-base ml-1 text-[var(--text-muted)] font-medium\">bank partners</span></p><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-foreground tracking-tight\">Home loans from 90+ banks</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed\">We pre-negotiate rates and surface your best offer in 48 hours — without the usual broker runaround. Pick the terms that suit you; we handle approvals.</p></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-3 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-white p-7 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start gap-5\" style=\"box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\" style=\"background:var(--accent)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-slot=\"icon\" class=\"w-5 h-5\" style=\"color:var(--primary)\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 0 0 2.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 0 0 4.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 0 0-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 0 1 8.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0 1 11.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 1 1-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 0 1 6.75 0Zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 1 1-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 0 1 5.25 0Z\"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-foreground tracking-tight\">Trusted across Bangalore</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed\">Families in Whitefield, HSR Layout, Koramangala, Indiranagar, and Sarjapur have transferred safely with Jumbo SafeBuy. Fixed prices, no hidden commissions.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"product-demo\" class=\"section-wrapper bg-[var(--background)]\"><div class=\"container-lg px-6 md:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12 lg:mb-16\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><span class=\"eyebrow\">See it in action</span><h2 class=\"mt-4 text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground text-balance max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Your deal, live on your phone</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-lg text-[var(--text-secondary)] max-w-xl mx-auto text-balance\">From token to keys — every step tracked, every party verified, every rupee accounted for.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0\"><ol class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\" style=\"list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0\"><li><button class=\"w-full text-left rounded-2xl transition-all\" style=\"padding:16px 18px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 20%, transparent);box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);cursor:pointer;position:relative;display:block\" aria-current=\"step\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"position:absolute;left:0;top:16px;bottom:16px;width:3px;border-radius:2px;background:var(--primary);transition:background 200ms ease\"></div><p style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--primary);margin:0;transition:color 200ms ease\">01 · Deal initiated</p><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:var(--foreground);margin:4px 0 0;letter-spacing:-0.015em;line-height:1.3\">Buyer and seller, verified and locked in</p><div style=\"overflow:hidden;height:auto;opacity:1\"><p style=\"font-size:13.5px;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:8px 0 0;line-height:1.5\">Both parties complete KYC in under a minute. We pull the property listing, confirm terms, and prep the escrow rails.</p></div></button></li><li><button class=\"w-full text-left rounded-2xl transition-all\" style=\"padding:16px 18px;background:transparent;border:1px solid transparent;box-shadow:none;cursor:pointer;position:relative;display:block\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"position:absolute;left:0;top:16px;bottom:16px;width:3px;border-radius:2px;background:transparent;transition:background 200ms ease\"></div><p style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-muted);margin:0;transition:color 200ms ease\">02 · Funds in escrow</p><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:4px 0 0;letter-spacing:-0.015em;line-height:1.3\">Your money sits with an RBI-licensed partner</p><div style=\"overflow:hidden;height:0px;opacity:0\"><p style=\"font-size:13.5px;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:8px 0 0;line-height:1.5\">Zero release until every condition clears — title check, agreement signed, sub-registrar filing. Refundable if anything falls through.</p></div></button></li><li><button class=\"w-full text-left rounded-2xl transition-all\" style=\"padding:16px 18px;background:transparent;border:1px solid transparent;box-shadow:none;cursor:pointer;position:relative;display:block\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"position:absolute;left:0;top:16px;bottom:16px;width:3px;border-radius:2px;background:transparent;transition:background 200ms ease\"></div><p style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-muted);margin:0;transition:color 200ms ease\">03 · Agreement signed</p><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:4px 0 0;letter-spacing:-0.015em;line-height:1.3\">Drafted, reviewed, and e-signed in hours</p><div style=\"overflow:hidden;height:0px;opacity:0\"><p style=\"font-size:13.5px;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:8px 0 0;line-height:1.5\">Our lawyers draft the sale agreement. Both parties sign online with witnessed timestamps. No printouts, no back-and-forth.</p></div></button></li><li><button class=\"w-full text-left rounded-2xl transition-all\" style=\"padding:16px 18px;background:transparent;border:1px solid transparent;box-shadow:none;cursor:pointer;position:relative;display:block\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"position:absolute;left:0;top:16px;bottom:16px;width:3px;border-radius:2px;background:transparent;transition:background 200ms ease\"></div><p style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-muted);margin:0;transition:color 200ms ease\">04 · Deal closed</p><p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:4px 0 0;letter-spacing:-0.015em;line-height:1.3\">Registration filed. Keys handed over.</p><div style=\"overflow:hidden;height:0px;opacity:0\"><p style=\"font-size:13.5px;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:8px 0 0;line-height:1.5\">We draft the sale deed, pay stamp duty, coordinate the sub-registrar, and transfer khata. Funds release to seller on your signal.</p></div></button></li></ol></div><div class=\"flex justify-center lg:justify-end\"><div class=\"relative w-full max-w-[320px] rounded-[2.6rem] p-[10px]\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(155deg, #454548 0%, #2c2c2e 28%, #1a1a1c 62%, #0d0d0f 100%);box-shadow:0 2px 0 rgb(255 255 255 / 0.14) inset,\n          0 -1px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 0.45) inset,\n          0 55px 100px -25px rgb(10 37 64 / 0.28),\n          0 35px 70px -35px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.45),\n          0 0 0 1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.35)\"><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-[2px] rounded-[2.45rem] opacity-[0.14]\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(125deg, rgb(255 255 255 / 0.55) 0%, transparent 42%, transparent 100%)\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2.1rem] bg-[var(--background)] font-sans antialiased flex flex-col\" style=\"aspect-ratio:9 / 19.5;box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px rgb(10 37 64 / 0.06),\n            inset 0 1px 0 rgb(255 255 255 / 0.75)\"><div class=\"absolute left-1/2 top-[9px] z-20 h-[26px] w-[96px] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-black\" style=\"box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.35), inset 0 1px 0 rgb(255 255 255 / 0.08)\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex items-center justify-between px-5 pt-[14px] pb-[6px]\"><span class=\"text-[11px] font-semibold tabular-nums tracking-tight\" style=\"color:var(--foreground)\">9:41</span><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><div class=\"flex gap-[2px]\" style=\"color:var(--foreground)\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"w-[2.5px] rounded-[1px] bg-current\" style=\"height:3.5px;opacity:0.35\"></div><div class=\"w-[2.5px] rounded-[1px] bg-current\" style=\"height:5.3px;opacity:0.55\"></div><div class=\"w-[2.5px] rounded-[1px] bg-current\" style=\"height:7.1px;opacity:0.85\"></div><div class=\"w-[2.5px] rounded-[1px] bg-current\" style=\"height:8.9px;opacity:1\"></div></div><div class=\"ml-1 flex h-[9px] w-[20px] items-center justify-end rounded-[2.5px] border px-[1.5px]\" style=\"border-color:var(--foreground)\"><div class=\"h-[5.5px] w-[55%] rounded-[1px]\" style=\"background:var(--foreground)\"></div></div></div></div><div style=\"padding:6px 14px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);background:#ffffff\"><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:8px\"><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px\"><div style=\"width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:6px;background:color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 14%, transparent);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-slot=\"icon\" style=\"width:13px;height:13px;color:var(--primary)\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M8.25 21v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21m0 0h4.5V3.545M12.75 21h7.5V10.75M2.25 21h1.5m18 0h-18M2.25 9l4.5-1.636M18.75 3l-1.5.545m0 6.205 3 1m1.5.5-1.5-.5M6.75 7.364V3h-3v18m3-13.636 10.5-3.819\"></path></svg></div><div><p style=\"font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--foreground);margin:0;line-height:1.1\">Transaction</p><p style=\"font-size:9px;color:var(--text-muted);margin:0;font-family:monospace;letter-spacing:0.02em\">#TXN-9821</p></div></div><span style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;background:color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 14%, transparent);color:var(--primary);border:1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 22%, transparent);border-radius:999px;padding:2px 9px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.04em;text-transform:uppercase;white-space:nowrap\">In Progress</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:4px\" role=\"tablist\" aria-label=\"Demo steps\"><button role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-label=\"Go to Initiated\" style=\"flex:1;height:3px;border-radius:2px;background:var(--border);border:none;padding:0;cursor:pointer;overflow:hidden;position:relative\"><div style=\"height:100%;width:0%;background:var(--primary);transition:width 90ms linear\"></div></button><button role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-label=\"Go to Escrow\" style=\"flex:1;height:3px;border-radius:2px;background:var(--border);border:none;padding:0;cursor:pointer;overflow:hidden;position:relative\"><div style=\"height:100%;width:0%;background:var(--primary);transition:width 90ms linear\"></div></button><button role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-label=\"Go to Agreement\" style=\"flex:1;height:3px;border-radius:2px;background:var(--border);border:none;padding:0;cursor:pointer;overflow:hidden;position:relative\"><div style=\"height:100%;width:0%;background:var(--primary);transition:width 90ms linear\"></div></button><button role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-label=\"Go to Closed\" style=\"flex:1;height:3px;border-radius:2px;background:var(--border);border:none;padding:0;cursor:pointer;overflow:hidden;position:relative\"><div style=\"height:100%;width:0%;background:var(--primary);transition:width 90ms linear\"></div></button></div></div><div style=\"flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;min-height:0;position:relative\"><div style=\"flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;padding:8px 14px 12